Package edu.mills.cs180a.mathdatabase

Classes demonstrating the use of asyncTask for a lecture in CS 180A: Mobile Application Development at Mills College.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InsertSquaresAsyncTask
    Insert a range of rows into the TABLE_SQUARES table of the database created in MathDatabaseOpenHelper.
    MainActivity
    An activity that enables a user to add or delete data from table TABLE_SQUARES of the database opened by MathDatabaseOpenHelper.
    MathDatabaseOpenHelper
    A helper to create a database with a single table holding integer values and their squares.
